export default {
  lift: {
    key: "lift",
    title: "Lift",
    subtitle: "Winner at Hack the North 2018",
    description: "Fitbit Ionic app to track repetitions during workouts. My focus was developing and designing the user interface of the app and the design of the product and dashboard.",
    devpost: "https://devpost.com/software/lift-ilm43c",
    github: "https://github.com/ariellam/lift",
    image: "https://i.imgur.com/6ncLjUr.png",
    imageHover: "https://i.imgur.com/D8JmMgi.png"
  },
  describe: {
    key: "describe",
    title: "deScribe",
    subtitle: "UofTHacks 2019",
    description: "A mental health chatbot that allows you to journal out loud. Using DialogFlow and Google Assistant, we were able to process the user's thoughts and give advice based on their mood.",

    github: "https://github.com/ariellam/SmartJournalAssistant",
    image: "https://i.imgur.com/N9NT3bK.png",

  },
  givingtree: {
    key: "givingtree",
    title: "GivingTree",
    subtitle: "Winner at The Lady Hacks 2016",

    devpost: "https://devpost.com/software/givingtreeapp",
    github: "https://github.com/ariellam/GivingTreeApp",
    image: "https://i.imgur.com/kWD9zp8.png",
    imageHover: "https://i.imgur.com/8wSWfLq.png"
